reviewText: This movie is pretty good! I saw it for the first time when I was in 3rd grade and I still watch it quite often. I still think its funny though that the same people who made Faces of Death made this movie. Maybe thats why  there is all of the attack scenes...
I have been watching this movie since I was a kid and I've never gotten tired of it,especially part 1,you need to buy it. I know for a fact you won't regret it!!!
